     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"Word is those 200/10 Fennin-bane weapons the GMs passed around may have had something to do with it."</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
